        <title>Legal Interrogation Procedures Act</title>
      </item>
      <item>
        <titleType>Official Title as Introduced</titleType>
        <title>To require the intelligence community to use only methods of interrogation authorized by the United States Army Field Manual on Human Intelligence Collector Operations.</title>
